{"tid":2175094,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[好似無人講，我講] 721今朝拉咗個銀行副總裁","createTime":"2020-08-26T09:56:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T10:49:32.000Z","uid":125223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a551ed55642742a8f40d042b937a11a9dca01d6e","tid":2175094,"uid":125223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T09:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tPKc2Up.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtPKc2Up.png&h=a23e9382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方拘捕民主黨立法會議員林卓廷及許智峯等16人，涉及去年721元朗暴力襲擊事件及7月6日屯門警署外，涉嫌暴動及企圖妨礙司法公正等。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，今次就721事件拘捕13人，年齡由26至48歲，全部涉及參與暴動，包括林卓廷，其他人報稱是<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">銀行副總裁</span></span>、社工、廚師、倉務司機等，部份人有黑社會背景。全部人正被扣留調查。警方指，相信13人屬衝突中，與早前被捕的44人另一派的人士。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷同時涉及兩宗案件，而許智峯涉及屯門警署外的案件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2354230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2354230&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatl3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=7e30bf1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2354230</a><br />\n<br />\n有無人講下係幾高層？"},{"pid":"f14a1d9c507d81b711591057c096a663d8e4c8ec","tid":2175094,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:40:43.000Z","msg":"想知邊間銀行"},{"pid":"84b914e5b8e83dbe6be13f111c8f2185bea3e6fc","tid":2175094,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:43:35.000Z","msg":"恐嚇唔好制裁？"},{"pid":"4d3c24d0c9e05708d0dd2081cda535d2c65d7d12","tid":2175094,"uid":182653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:46:00.000Z","msg":"vp 好低級， sales 的話"},{"pid":"8d4e05c1e84d8cd8e30d4dcee3ee46c3b022827f","tid":2175094,"uid":172500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:46:25.000Z","msg":"舉例 獅子銀行rm title 已經係副總裁<br />\n其實唔係好高級<br />\n其他銀行都類似"},{"pid":"25d8759c1bdd97d7c1c374c93a20a7192a08cd07","tid":2175094,"uid":63866,"l